CustomField.description: The allocated value of Superannuation based on the nominated distribution in this record
CustomField.formula: If ( RecordType.DeveloperName = 'Withholding_Superannuation' , If ( AND ( tc9_pr__Distribution_Amount__c <> 0 , NOT ( ISBLANK ( tc9_pr__Distribution_Amount__c ) ) ) , tc9_pr__Distribution_Amount__c , ROUND ( ( tc9_pr__Pay_Transaction__r.tc9_pr__Superannuation_Guarantee__c + tc9_pr__Pay_Transaction__r.tc9_pr__Superannuation_Employer_Additional__c ) * tc9_pr__Distribution_Percentage__c , 2 ) ) , 0 )
CustomField.inlineHelpText: The allocated value of Superannuation based on the nominated distribution in this record
CustomField.label: Superannuation Value
